{
  "page": "Edgerran Oakheart",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\"><img alt=\"House Oakheart.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/50px-House_Oakheart.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/75px-House_Oakheart.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/100px-House_Oakheart.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Edgerran Oakheart<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Open-Handed</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\"><img alt=\"House Oakheart.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/50px-House_Oakheart.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/75px-House_Oakheart.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Oakheart.svg/100px-House_Oakheart.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nEdgerran the Open-Handed</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Old_Oak\" title=\"Lord of Old Oak\">Lord of Old Oak</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\">House Oakheart</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Edgerran Oakheart</b>, better known as <b>Edgerran the Open-Handed</b>, was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Oak\" title=\"Old Oak\">Old Oak</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\">House Oakheart</a> at an unknown time.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Legacy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Legacy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edgerran_Oakheart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Edgerran fought against <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Legacy\">Legacy</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edgerran_Oakheart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Legacy\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>There is a <a href=\"/index.php/Tapestry\" title=\"Tapestry\">tapestry</a> of Edgerran at Old Oak depicting him sitting with a hundred Dornishmen heads piled around his feet.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edgerran_Oakheart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edgerran_Oakheart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arys_Oakheart\" title=\"Arys Oakheart\">Arys Oakheart</a> thought of Lord Edgerran and the Oakheart traditon of killing Dornishmen while walking the streets of <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edgerran_Oakheart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_13\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 13\">Chapter 13</a>, The Soiled Knight.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Old_Oak\" title=\"Lord of Old Oak\">Lord of Old Oak</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Torgen_Oakheart\" title=\"Torgen Oakheart\">Torgen Oakheart</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404170034\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usag